{"tid":882924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷念金庸，一齊傾吓佢啲作品","createTime":"2018-10-30T12:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T12:26:40.000Z","uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfcff26faaa09b6c75a5dd324a2adfc8d2e7ba2","tid":882924,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"草委查良鏞與查濟民1988年11月拋出一個被認為是北京官方想法的「協調方案」，供《基本法》草委及諮委討論。[1]方案內容建議立法會分三屆發展到半數直選；而第二任及第三位行政長官由800人組成的選委選出，正正是1997年後特區政制發展的安排。查氏方案中關於第三任行政長官任內，進行一次全體選民投票，以決定第四任行政長官是否普選，以及第五屆以後的立法會是否全面直選的提議，則未有寫入《基本法》內。<br />\n====================================================<br />\n一齊傾吓渣生作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9p1yTvv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9p1yTvv.png&h=c4cd69d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCYp0av.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCYp0av.png&h=1a34a134&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56894b1aac4ec02331139666aee7509ebc8a3ae4","tid":882924,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T12:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}